Manage Linear credentials

Usage:
  agentflow auth linear [command]

Available Commands:
  list        List stored Linear credentials
  login       Validate and store a Linear API key
  logout      Delete the stored Linear API key
  status      Show how the Linear API key resolves

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for linear

Global Flags:
      --repo string   Path inside the repo to operate on

Use "agentflow auth linear [command] --help" for more information about a command.
